原告不公。律政司另須為是次申請支付堂費。<br />\n<br />\n律政司一方又問李認為警員制服時的行為是否合法，再被法官阻止，指問題不應由證人回答，合法與否應由法庭裁定，否則別人會認為法官失職。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/H2ZWUG46ZZEXJAHJHW5SMZDZ2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2FH2ZWUG46ZZEXJAHJHW5SMZDZ2I%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11N9ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=e0adafd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2FH2ZWUG46ZZEXJAHJHW5SMZDZ2I%2F&h=a3eb45b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/H2ZWUG46ZZEXJAHJHW5SMZDZ2I/</a>"},{"pid":"9699d32bef74153a280c5367fb88b0a42d87c07f","tid":2487089,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351091905e5cbbf8c6c0ac109794ea32ab92d751","tid":2487089,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>律政司一方又問李認為警員制服時的行為是否合法，再被法官阻止，指問題不應由證人回答，合法與否應由法庭裁定，否則別人會認為法官失職。</blockquote><br />\n邊隻垃圾律正狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺撚到明係唔合法先告鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}